data.description: Discover the essence of rustic elegance in this charming farmhouse nestled on 25 sprawling acres. A true blend of nostalgia and modern living awaits you in this custom-designed home. As you step inside, the great room welcomes you with its soaring wood ceiling, creating an atmosphere of spaciousness and warmth. The focal point, a magnificent mountain stone fireplace, beckons you to gather around and create memories with loved ones. The heart of this home is the kitchen, with a central island and gleaming stainless steel appliances. Adjacent to it, a cozy breakfast nook and a separate dining area provide the perfect settings for enjoying delicious meals. Step outside, and you'll find a fenced garden area, an outdoor enthusiast's dream. Whether you're grilling up a feast or simply relaxing, this space is designed for your enjoyment. A tranquil water garden adds a touch of serenity to the landscape. This home is not only charming but eco-friendly, too, with solar panels that make it energy-efficient. Practicality meets passion in the 3-bay workshop - 35 x 50, offering ample space for your creative endeavors or hobbies. With 5 bedrooms and 2 baths, there's room for the whole family. Covered porches on both levels invite you to take in the picturesque surroundings. A touch of nostalgia and modern convenience come together seamlessly in the attached carport and garage. Experience the allure of country living on 25 acres, some of which are cleared for farming. This home is more than just a house; it's a lifestyle. Embrace the character and comfort of this farmhouse. Enjoy the reality of owning your own farm in rural north Georgia. Located within 30-45 min to Ringgold, Chattanooga or Dalton.
